|passage=From the ground, Colombo’s port does not look like much.{{...}} But viewed from high up in one of the growing number of skyscrapers in Sri Lanka’s capital, it is clear that something extraordinary is happening: China is '''creating''' a shipping hub just 200 miles from India’s southern tip.}}
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[design]], [[invest]] with a [[new]] form, shape, etc.
#: {{ux|en|Couturiers '''create''' exclusive garments for an affluent clientele.}}
#* {{quote-journal|date=2013-06-21|author={{w|Oliver Burkeman}}
